object.customQuery:
SELECT address_key,address_line,
    SPLIT_PART(address_line, ',', 1) AS Address_Line1,
    SPLIT_PART(address_line, ',', 2) AS Address_Line2,
    SPLIT_PART(address_line, ',', 3) AS Address_Line3,
    SPLIT_PART(address_line, ',', 4) AS Address_Line4,
    SPLIT_PART(address_line, ',', 5) AS CITY,
    SPLIT_PART(address_line, ',', 6) AS STATE,
    SPLIT_PART(address_line, ',', 7) AS ZIP_CODE
FROM dbo.lkp_address_key where address_key in (select address_Key from (SELECT address_key, LENGTH(address_line) - LENGTH(REPLACE(address_line, ',', '')) AS comma_count
                      from dbo.lkp_address_key
  where comma_count=6)) and Address_key not in (select AddressKey AS LKP_Address_key from dbo.addressdetail) ;
